HEADWORD: Magnoliaceous
<hw>Mag*no`li*a"ceous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Pertaining to a natural order (<ord>Magnoliaceae</ord>) of trees of
which the magnolia, the tulip tree, and the star anise are
examples.</def>⟦br⟧
